	<h1 class="title">移动支付发展如此，拉卡拉的失败几乎在情理之中</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/553548/small/553548.jpg?1459925608" alt="">
